data.name: RichTextBox1.Text
data.value:
Health Kiosk device will get your health data non-invasively. This application will assist you to use the device by yourself and check out your health parameters. These parameters are taken non-invasively and displayed at the end of the process. The following parameters will be manipulated from the user,
1. Heart rate. 2. Blood sugar level. 3. Body temperature. 4. Blood pressure. 5. Mental stress.
Click Next to follow instruction that will guide you to measure the physiological parameters.

data.name: RichTextBox2.Text
data.value:
It’s time for you to use the kiosk kit. First connect the kit with power supply. Secondly use the kit to get your health data, if you are struck at any of the parameters then go to that specific parameter and review them again. Once you have finished using the kit, click the Next button to view your health data.
And once again if you finish using the kit properly, click the Next button to view your current health result.
